resoFacts.subdivisionName: CANDELIGHT ESTATES 3 LOTS 1 THROUGH 54 & TRACT A

data.description: Discover your forever sanctuary in the highly sought-after CANDLELIGHT ESTATES community. This splendid residence boasts 4 bed/2 bath on a spacious corner lot. The kitchen is a culinary haven, complete w/ elegant cabinetry, a walk-in pantry, granite countertops, & stainless steel appliances, complemented by a formal dining area.Unwind in the formal living room or cozy up in the family room by the fireplace. Revel in the 9-foot ceilings, four generously sized bedrooms with newer carpeting & refreshed neutral-toned paint. The bonus room, equipped w/ climate control, offers endless possibilities, serving as a storage area, an extra bedroom, or a versatile office or hobby space.Outside, a covered patio and RV gate await, along w/ sparkling diving pool. With NO HOA restrictions
